        "action": "Ban plastic drink bottles, to use glass or cans only",
        "additional_details": "To be more proactive, to stop the single use culture, to make people more aware of the damage that plastic bottles are doing to our environment, bottles being washed up on coastal shore lines, polluting our rivers, littering our countryside, mountain tops and everywhere in our villages, towns and cities.",
        "background": "To put an end of the damage that plastic drinking bottles and bottle caps are doing to our environment, the litter created by the single use culture is a disease that needs to end.",
